  "title": "Waitakere Ranges Regional Park: Omanawanui Track",
  "summary": "喜欢摄影的朋友推荐这个沙滩拍彗星。但是我离家很远，没有条件在日落时分来拍彗星。我只能周末白天来旁边走走。 步道 […]",
  "content": "<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-184.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>喜欢摄影的朋友推荐这个沙滩拍彗星。但是我离家很远，没有条件在日落时分来拍彗星。我只能周末白天来旁边走走。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-181.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>步道周边的景色很美。又没多少人。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-187.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>大部分的步道都有树荫，不是很热。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-182.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>看起来不远的对岸，要开车绕一个多小时才能到。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-183.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>鸟瞰海滩。很漂亮的弧形。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-185.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>",
  "image": "https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-184.png",
